    "html_format": "<div class=\"document-view-wrapper\">\n<style>\n.html-preview * {font-family: Times New Roman; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview a.NoteRef {text-decoration: none;}\n.html-preview table td {vertical-align: top;}\n.html-preview table {width: 100%;}\n.html-preview p {white-space: pre-wrap;}\n.html-preview .leading {width: 4px; display: inline-block;}\n.html-preview hr {height: 1px; padding: 0; margin: 1em 0; border: 0; border-top: 1px solid #CCC;}\n.html-preview .a {font-family: 'Times New Roman'; font-size: 12pt;}\n.html-preview .a3 td {border: 1px solid #000;}\n</style>\n<div class=\"html-preview\">\n<style>.html-preview{width: 762px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-top: 76px}</style><style>.html-preview{margin-bottom: 32px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-left: 81px}</style><style>.html-preview{padding-right: 57px}</style><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-2\" style=\"color: #000000; text-transform: uppercase;\">{#2}Шартнома рақами</span><span style=\"color: #000000; text-transform: uppercase;\"> -сон МЕҲНАТ ШАРТНОМАСИ (КОНТРАКТ)</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-3\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#3}Шартнома тузилган ҳудуд</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">‎<span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span></span><span class=\"structures structure-4\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#4}Шартнома тузилган сана</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">‎‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">1. Корхона (мулкчиликнинг барча шаклларидаги ташкилот, муассаса, шу жумладан, уларнинг алоҳида таркибий бўлинмалари </span><span class=\"structures structure-7\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#7}Иш берувчининг тўлиқ номи ва раҳбарининг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> тўлиқ номи‎ номидан, кейинги ўринларда «Иш берувчи» деб аталади ва фуқаро </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#8}Ходимнинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> кейинги ўринларда «Ходим» деб аталади, мазкур шартномани қуйидагилар ҳақида туздик:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">2. Ходим </span><span class=\"structures structure-8\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#8}Ходимнинг Ф.И.О.</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> </span><span class=\"structures structure-11\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#11}Таклиф қилинаетган иш жой</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> ‎‎‎‎‎‎касби бўйича </span><span class=\"structures structure-12\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#12}Таклиф қилинаётган лавозим номи ва талаблари</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> ‎‎‎‎‎лавозимига ишга қабул қилинади. ‎‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">3. Шартнома </span><span class=\"structures structure-13\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#13}Иш вақти тури</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">‎<span class=\"leading\"></span>‎‎‎ҳисобланади.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">4. Шартнома муддати </span><span class=\"structures structure-14\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#14}Шартнома муддати</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">‎‎‎.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">5. Шартнома бўйича ишлаш бошланиши </span><span class=\"structures structure-15\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#15}Шартнома кучга кириш вақти</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> тамом бўлиши</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-16\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#16}Шартнома якунига етиш вақти</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">6. Синов муддати </span><span class=\"structures structure-17\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#17}Синов муддати</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">7. Ходимнинг мажбуриятлари:‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">а) меҳнат ва технология интизоми (ички меҳнат тартиби қоидалари, уставлар ва интизом тўғрисидаги қоидалар)га риоя қилиш;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">б) иш берувчининг қонуний фармойишларини бажариш;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">в) меҳнатни муҳофаза қилиш, хавфсизлик техникаси ва ишлаб чиқариш санитарияси талабларига риоя қилиш;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">г) лавозим йўриқномаларига риоя қилиш;‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">д) ЯТММ, ММ билан назарда тутилган малака мажбуриятларига риоя қилиш;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">е) қонун ҳужжатлари ва бошқа норматив ҳужжатларга риоя қилиш;‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">ж) жамоа шартномаси шартларига риоя қилиш;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">з) ходим томонидан қабул қилинадиган бошқа мажбуриятлар.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-18\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#18}Ходимнинг мажбуриятлари</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">8. Иш берувчининг мажбуриятлари;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">а) ходимнинг меҳнатини ташкил этиш, ходимни Меҳнатни муҳофаза қилиш ва хавфсизлик техникаси қоидалари, лавозим йўриқномалари, жамоа шартномаси ва бошқа норматив ва маҳаллий ҳужжатлар билан таништириш;‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">б) меҳнат ва ишлаб чиқариш интизомини таъминлаш;‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">в) иш ҳақини ўз вақтида тўлаш;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">г) хавфсиз ва самарали меҳнат учун шарт-шароитлар яратиш, ходимни ўқитиш, унга меҳнатнинг хавфсиз шарт-шароити тўғрисида йўл-йўриқ бериш;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">д) иш жойини меҳнатни муҳофаза қилиш ва хавфсизлик техникаси қоидаларига мувофиқ жиҳозлаш;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">ж) қонун ҳужжатларига ва бошқа норматив ҳужжатларга риоя қилиш;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">з) жамоа шартномаси шартларига риоя қилиш;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">и) иш берувчи томонидан қабул қилинадиган бошқа мажбуриятлар:‎ ‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Иш берувчининг мажбуриятлари</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">9. Иш куни режими </span><span class=\"structures structure-19\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#19}Иш куни режими</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">10. Меҳнат ҳақи тўлаш.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Ходимга қуйидагича ҳаҳ тўлаш белгиланади:‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">а) </span><span class=\"structures structure-21\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#21}Тўлов тури ва миқдори</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">б) амалдаги қонун ҳужжатларига ва норматив ҳужжатларга мувофиқ меҳнат шароитлари билан боғлиқ бўлган қўшимча ҳақ, устама, компенсациялар қуйидаги миқдорларда: ‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#22}Қўшимча ҳақ тўлаш тури</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#23}Қўшимча ҳақ тўлаш миқдори</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">в) жамоа шартномаси шартлари билан назарда тутилган, шунингдек, берилган</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">(мавжуд) ҳуқуқлар ва маблағлар доирасида раҳбар томонидан белгиланадиган қўшимча ҳақ, устама,</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">мукофот, тақдирлашлар ва рағбатлантирувчи турдаги бошқа тўловлар;</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-22\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#22}Қўшимча ҳақ тўлаш тури</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span class=\"structures structure-23\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#23}Қўшимча ҳақ тўлаш миқдори</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">11. Ходимга:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">а) асосий таътил (меҳнат таътили) </span><span class=\"structures structure-24\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#24}Асосий таътил муддати</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> иш кунидан;‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">б) қўшимча таътил </span><span class=\"structures structure-25\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#25}Қўшимча таътил муддати</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\"> иш кунидан иборат бўлган ҳақ тўланадиган йиллик таътил белгиланади.‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify; text-indent: 45.6px;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">12. Меҳнат шартномаси (контракт)нинг меҳнат шароитлари ва унга ҳақ тўлаш хусусиятлари, ижтимоий ҳимоя, имтиёзлар, кафолатлар ва ҳоказолар билан боғлиқ бўлган бошқа шартлари.</span></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><span style=\"color: #000000;\">Томонларнинг манзиллари ва имзолари:</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">‎</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000; font-weight: bold;\">Иш берувчи:‎ <span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span><span class=\"leading\"></span>‎Ходим:</span><span style=\"color: #000000;\">‎</span></p>\n<table>\n<tr>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 318.1163434903px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-31\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#31}Иш берувчининг тўлиқ номи</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-32\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#32}Иш берувчининг манзили</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-33\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#33}Шартнома тузилган сана</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">(муҳр) __________(имзо)</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p>\n</td>\n<td 0=\"\" style=\" width: 318.18282548476px;\">\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-27\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#27}Ходимнинг Ф.И.О.</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-28\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#28}Ходимнинг манзили</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span class=\"structures structure-29\" style=\"color: #000000;\">{#29}Шартнома тузилган сана</span></p>\n<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: #000000;\">________ (имзо)</span></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</table>\n<p style=\"text-align